data.title: Fallen Angels Original 1995 French Grande Movie Poster
data.meta_description: Original 1995 French grande poster for the film Fallen Angels directed by Kar Wai Wong with Leon Lai / Michelle Reis / Takeshi Kaneshiro / Charlie Yeung. Fine condition, folded. Many original posters were issued folded or were subsequently folded.
